Module downfall
Package downfall.ui.editor

Class RealmEditorController

  • java.lang.Object
    • downfall.ui.editor.RealmEditorController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StageController
    public class RealmEditorController
extends java.lang.Object
implements StageController
    Controller class for the Realm Editor. It is responsible for the creation of new Realms. Controls /fxml/editors/RealmEditor.fxml and is annotated with @FXML where it references that FXML file.
